{"tid":1863884,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真係要去到搶廁紙？ （陰謀論）","createTime":"2020-02-05T10:33:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T11:39:45.000Z","uid":128415,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"968b9d916bcef6d4aa1dc9e5ec528667c062f75e","tid":1863884,"uid":128415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T10:33:42.000Z","msg":"搶完口罩 搶完野食 而家又開始講到無哂廁紙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到底係真係會無哂廁紙呀 定開始有人做到香港原來好缺乏物資 <br />\n<br />\n一旦無左大陸的支持 或者大陸有咩事呀<br />\n 即使香港本身有幾多外來物資 都無用嫁 因為經已在口罩之後 做到啲人驚左呀 驚會無哂 個個都囤積<br />\n 原本夠香港用 都變成唔夠用 唔好唔記得 玩弄人性一隻係佢哋嘅強項 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重有多謝一班炒狗 同班成家中哂武漢肺炎的騙子 令到香港雪上加霜 祝你地長命百歲 百病纏身 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1085b3376330543d4bcab971155f3617eb3929d1","tid":1863884,"uid":300679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T10:44:55.000Z","msg":"促銷成功"},{"pid":"6a241bce7499ab4b403ae5128e423b11704f43e8","tid":1863884,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T10:54:25.000Z","msg":"連登仔不嬲都支持嫁啦"},{"pid":"2a29e6512f0945d6f7c309daafeaa063b0082e94","tid":1863884,"uid":123848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:08:17.000Z","msg":"下次搶水搶油搶M巾搶安全套"},{"pid":"6db3ebdbb071266d577270341185ebdd2531bb37","tid":1863884,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:16:24.000Z","msg":"食幾多，疴幾多，係整定"},{"pid":"24d90602a41c4e2003b16c74e94d3c65f109fc38","tid":1863884,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:25:21.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"505db1265c5c9c80c20887d8ad1ed080446b636e","tid":1863884,"uid":128415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:39:45.000Z","msg":"見到啲人係咁搶 又跑去找廁紙 認真一諗真係笑唔出 <br />\n香港人比撚狗咁撚.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}